name: SubnetNetworkAclAssociation
shortDesc: Associates a subnet with a network ACL.

properties.name: SubnetId
properties.desc: The ID representing the current association between the original network ACL and the subnet.

properties.name: NetworkAclId
properties.desc: The ID of the new ACL to associate with the subnet.

attributes.name: AssociationId
attributes.desc: Returns the value of this object's SubnetId property.
